    "description": "<p>PHARMENG TECHNOLOGY PTE. LTD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PharmEng Technology is a fully integrated multinational consultiany serving the pharmaceutical and life science industries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our GMP compliance services include commissioning and qualification, validation, quality systems, engineering, auditing, process development, technology transfer, and professional training.  We specialize in compliance to US FDA, EU GMP, Health Canada, PIC/S GMP, and WHO GMP regulations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our regulatory services include pre- and post-market marketing authorization, license holding, maintenance, reporting, compliance, and adverse event handling in East and Southeast Asia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>PharmEng currently operates permanently in US, Canada, Singapore, Taiwan, and Malaysia, plus projects around the world.</p>\r\n",
